    <title>长摘要-宏观经济感知、货币政策与微观企业投融资行为</title>
    <link>http://localhost:1313/research/%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%84%9F%E7%9F%A5%E8%B4%A7%E5%B8%81%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E4%B8%8E%E5%BE%AE%E8%A7%82%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E6%8A%95%E8%9E%8D%E8%B5%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA/</link>
